This repository holds some test scripts being used by the linux-wpan project
during development and testing.



wpan-tools:

ieee802154:
o Sending ieee802154 frames back and forth with wpan-ping

6lowpan:
o Some basic ping6 testing with various sizes
o Plugtest stimuli as defined in https://github.com/6lo/test-descriptions and
  being used in various ETSI plugfests for 6lo
